opied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent wide\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104nti1665702919111.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/nti1665702919111.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/nti1665702919111.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"nti1665702919111\" role=\"article\">\n<div class=\"body conbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Refer to the following header files that are used to build a Uniface database\n      connector. These files are located in the <span class=\"ph filepath\">/3gl/include</span> directory of the\n      Uniface installation.</p>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"nti1665702919111__table_d15401e1_d15402e1_d15403e1\"><caption><span class=\"table--title-label\">Table 1. </span><span class=\"title\">Header Files</span></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"nti1665702919111__table_d15401e1_d15402e1_d15403e1__entry__1\">Header File </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"nti1665702919111__table_d15401e1_d15402e1_d15403e1__entry__2\">Contents </th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"nti1665702919111__table_d15401e1_d15402e1_d15403e1__entry__1\"><span class=\"ph filepath\">unidbm.h</span>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"nti1665702919111__table_d15401e1_d15402e1_d15403e1__entry__2\">Public DBMS interface </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"nti1665702919111__table_d15401e1_d15402e1_d15403e1__entry__1\"><span class=\"ph filepath\">unityp.h</span>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"nti1665702919111__table_d15401e1_d15402e1_d15403e1__entry__2\">Uniface data types </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"nti1665702919111__table_d15401e1_d15402e1_d15403e1__entry__1\"><span class=\"ph filepath\">unipck.h</span>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"nti1665702919111__table_d15401e1_d15402e1_d15403e1__entry__2\">Uniface packing codes </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"nti1665702919111__table_d15401e1_d15402e1_d15403e1__entry__1\"><span class=\"ph filepath\">unistr.h</span>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"nti1665702919111__table_d15401e1_d15402e1_d15403e1__entry__2\">Uniface string function </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"nti1665702919111__table_d15401e1_d15402e1_d15403e1__entry__1\"><span class=\"ph filepath\">iccapi.h</span>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"nti1665702919111__table_d15401e1_d15402e1_d15403e1__entry__2\">DBMS Stored Procedures, via ICC API </td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"nti1665702919111__p_d129686e1_d129687e1_d129688e1\">On all platforms, a shared library needs to be linked\n         and fully resolved. This library is loaded by Uniface when needed. The following libraries\n         are used, in this order, to link a Uniface database connector.</p>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"nti1665702919111__table_d15404e1_d15405e1_d15406e1\"><caption><span class=\"table--title-label\">Table 2. </span><span class=\"title\">Microsoft Windows (located in<var class=\"keyword varname\">InstallDirectory</var>\n<span class=\"ph filepath\">/uniface/3gl/lib/</span>)</span></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"nti1665702919111__table_d15404e1_d15405e1_d15406e1__entry__1\">Library </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"nti1665702919111__table_d15404e1_d15405e1_d15406e1__entry__2\">Contents </th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"nti1665702919111__table_d15404e1_d15405e1_d15406e1__entry__1\"><span class=\"ph filepath\">umswlib.lib</span>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"nti1665702919111__table_d15404e1_d15405e1_d15406e1__entry__2\">Uniface/Microsoft Windows-specific </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"nti1665702919111__table_d15404e1_d15405e1_d15406e1__entry__1\"><span class=\"ph filepath\">urtl.lib</span>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"nti1665702919111__table_d15404e1_d15405e1_d15406e1__entry__2\">Uniface runtime system </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"nti1665702919111__table_d15404e1_d15405e1_d15406e1__entry__1\"><span class=\"ph filepath\">ulib.lib</span>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"nti1665702919111__table_d15404e1_d15405e1_d15406e1__entry__2\">Uniface library </td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"nti1665702919111__table_d15407e1_d15408e1_d15409e1\"><caption><span class=\"table--title-label\">Table 3. </span><span class=\"title\">Unix (located in<var class=\"keyword varname\">InstallDirectory</var>\n<span class=\"ph filepath\">/lib/</span>)</span></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"nti1665702919111__table_d15407e1_d15408e1_d15409e1__entry__1\">Library </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"nti1665702919111__table_d15407e1_d15408e1_d15409e1__entry__2\">Contents </th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"nti1665702919111__table_d15407e1_d15408e1_d15409e1__entry__1\"><span class=\"ph filepath\">libunis.a</span>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"nti1665702919111__table_d15407e1_d15408e1_d15409e1__entry__2\">Uniface/Unix-specific </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"nti1665702919111__table_d15407e1_d15408e1_d15409e1__entry__1\"><span class=\"ph filepath\">-lurtl</span>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"nti1665702919111__table_d15407e1_d15408e1_d15409e1__entry__2\">Uniface runtime system </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"nti1665702919111__table_d15407e1_d15408e1_d15409e1__entry__1\"><span class=\"ph filepath\">-lulib</span>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"nti1665702919111__table_d15407e1_d15408e1_d15409e1__entry__2\">Uniface library </td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2530419\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2530419\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "Database Connector Resources Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Jan 12, 2023 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Refer to the following header files that are used to build a Uniface database connector. These files are located in the /3gl/include directory of the Uniface installation. Table 1. Header Files Header File Contents unidbm.h Public DBMS interface unityp.h Uniface data types unipck.h Uniface packing codes unistr.h Uniface string function iccapi.h DBMS Stored Procedures, via ICC API On all platforms, a shared library needs to be linked and fully resolved. This library is loaded by Uniface when needed. The following libraries are used, in this order, to link a Uniface database connector. Table 2. Microsoft Windows (located in InstallDirectory /uniface/3gl/lib/ ) Library Contents umswlib.lib Uniface/Microsoft Windows-specific urtl.lib Uniface runtime system ulib.lib Uniface library Table 3. Unix (located in InstallDirectory /lib/ ) Library Contents libunis.a Uniface/Unix-specific -lurtl Uniface runtime system -lulib Uniface library Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}